# fixtures (planted suppressions, secrets, bare Errors, etc.) used to measure
# the scanner's precision/recall against a known oracle. Editing it must not be
# blocked by the very rules it exercises. These fixtures are CI artifacts only —
# never mirrored to dist/, never shipped.
skills/lawkeeper/evals/corpus/*
